{"tid":1327787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[明信片抗爭] 寄張「反送中」明信片給某國家的人","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:48.000Z","uid":1493,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"513b736fe7eb1f330af0b71b174785a222bb0459","tid":1327787,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.postcrossing.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.postcrossing.com&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsqjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=a93d10b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.postcrossing.com</a><br />\n<em>&quot;Postcrossing是一個在線計畫網站，人們可以透過此計劃和來自世界各地的人交換明信片。網站以&ldquo;寄張明信片給某國家的人，再從某國家的人那收到明信片吧！&rdquo;作為宣傳口號（英語: Send a postcard and receive a postcard back from a random person somewhere in the world!）[6]。參與本計劃的玩家稱為Postcrossers。<br />\n要寄出一張明信片，電腦會先隨機從世界各地抽選一位玩家的地址，並附上一組登錄編號。玩家必需將登錄編號寫上明信片，然後寄出。當對方已經收妥明信片，玩家隨後就會收到另一位隨機玩家寄出的明信片。每成功寄出一張明信片，就會成功收回一張。由於收寄來源不同，明信片的來源永遠是個驚喜。&quot;</em><br />\n<br />\n我希望大家一齊上網印刷大量包含「反送中」文宣既明信片，如圖畫，新聞圖片（立法會示威圖，救護車分紅海，城姐保護年青人，雨傘擋漼淚彈等等），文宣懶人包圖（英文），然後用英文簡短寫下香港而家發生緊咩事，例如點解用雨傘，什麼是送中條例，總之發揮創意，讓世界各地唔睇新聞既人都知道香港這個地方正在為守護自由而作戰。<br />\n<br />\n最後可唔可以有英文好既巴絲可以簡單寫幾句英文 template 比我地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4f4a3343a4d2948c9c827c480b364d3f115ff9","tid":1327787,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:35:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72471126fc793bf40f875061ad99241cffde4a82","tid":1327787,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47e0752e6129ff4e0e03f6c98f710e492f413836","tid":1327787,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90b52cb4d33ea81c58372e5e62d0481019f0b49b","tid":1327787,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e1f37613174f9daa22e96faf1c488d8d3e674a","tid":1327787,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9806ab88e7fee013c080c990b877f9f0b9f1a0bf","tid":1327787,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"151fcd82ca73c3c75461a24a1a7e3130b76bb752","tid":1327787,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:36:54.000Z","msg":"整條黑警片嘅q R code"},{"pid":"51ff9dae23c155f5fa33fcc24fc1f9a173488cc6","tid":1327787,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1583d7fdff8dbd6d665a8c661433f7b986186d15","tid":1327787,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"好唔好留小小位手寫有心意啲？<br />\n<br />\n但又好似有風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}